00:02:08.729 --> 00:02:12.620
So by far, the most common use
case for merchants at the

00:02:12.620 --> 00:02:14.930
Merchant Center is
order management.

00:02:14.930 --> 00:02:18.310
Merchants log in to get an idea
of the sales that are

00:02:18.310 --> 00:02:21.480
going on on our platform,
to actually look at the

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:24.960
individual orders, and to
perform any order management

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:28.160
functions such as charging the
order-- in the case of

00:02:28.160 --> 00:02:29.110
physical goods--

00:02:29.110 --> 00:02:32.870
or canceling the order, or
refunding the order in case of

00:02:32.870 --> 00:02:34.700
a customer complaint.

00:02:34.700 --> 00:02:37.780
