go and download reports.

00:02:37.780 --> 00:02:40.080
Say, for example, I wanted
to look at how many

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:41.280
orders I sold yesterday.

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:44.180
I could go and get a report that
would give me a list of

00:02:44.180 --> 00:02:46.980
all the orders that came through
the system yesterday.

00:02:46.980 --> 00:02:49.790
